content: Opening reception for Something Drawings series1 presented by Read the Room in Melbourne, Spencer Lai lecture performance of catalogue text.
DAVID BORG - BILLY BOB COULTHUR - ABELLA D'ADAMO -
ELLEN FAIRBAIRN - MADARA PAULA GRIÒšE - BRENNAN OLVER -

'Read the Room' is an expanded literary practice space focusing on writers and artists working both on and off the page. Co-directed by Kat Capel and Carmen Keiso, the initiative runs workshopping, reading, and exhibition events.
